headline: Could a Rotation Into Staples Stocks Be Next? What the Charts Say About 3 Dividend Payers.
summary: As the bull market rotates leadership across sectors, it may be time for consumer goods stocks to get their turn.  The consumer staples sector, a classic defensive play, has largely sat out the 2025 rally.

headline: Hon Hai Technology Group (Foxconn) Chief Procurement Officer Honored In Alcott Global's Top 30 Supply Chain Leaders of 2025
summary: Hon Hai Technology Group ("Foxconn") (TWSE:2317) announced that Chief Procurement Officer Max Chu has been recognized in the "Top 30 Supply Chain Leaders of 2025", a distinction organized by executive search firm Alcott Global honoring executives who are transforming global supply chains through innovation, leadership, and resilience.
